Agency Name: Department of Housing Preservation and Development
Resolution Description: The Department of Housing Preservation and Development was not able to gain access to your apartment or others in the building to inspect for a lack of heat or hot water. The complaint has been closed. If the condition still exists, please file a new complaint.
The Police Department responded to the complaint and took action to fix the condition.
The Department of Buildings investigated this complaint and determined that no further action was necessary.
